text: Scutellastra chapmani is a species of sea snail, a true limpet, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Patellidae, one of the families of true limpets. ==Description== ==Distribution== Scutellastra chapmani, ventral view ==References== Category:Patellidae Category:Gastropods described in 1875
title: Scutellastra chapmani
